import React from 'react' import { Icon, Label, Menu, Table } from 'semantic-ui-react' function print(row) { console.log(row.id); } const TableExamplePagination = (props) => ( Name Average Name Name Name {props.data.map((row) => ( {row.displayName} {row.average} {row.count} {row.firstUpdated} {row.lastUpdated} {row.lastValue} {row.unit} ))} {/* 1 2 3 4 */}
) export default TableExamplePagination
